SUMMARY:✅ FILED — IRS Form 1023-EZ (501(c)(3)) — $275 Paid
DESCRIPTION:Form 1023-EZ filed April 30\, 2026 — 27 days after incorporation.\n\nPay.gov Tracking ID: 281TLBGO\nAgency Tracking ID: 77374172589\nTransaction Amount: $275.00\nCard: Visa ****1203\nEIN: 42-1888158\n\nIRS typical processing: 2–6 months.\nExpected determination letter: July–October 2026.\n\nWHEN LETTER ARRIVES (within 30 days):\n1. File copy with GA Department of Revenue → state tax exemption\n2. File copy with GA SoS Securities & Charities Division (O.C.G.A. § 43-17-5)\n3. Post determination letter on phosphorus31.org/transparency\n4. Update IRS Form 990-N filing address if needed
END:VEVENT

